Categories: ["Orthopedic clinic","General practitioner","Occupational therapist","Orthopedic supplies store","Orthopedic surgeon","Pain management physician","Physiotherapist","Physiotherapy Center","Sports medicine physician"]
Description: Premier Bone & Joint Centers, located at 1909 Vista Drive in Laramie, Wyoming, is a state-of-the-art healthcare facility offering a comprehensive range of orthopedic and physical therapy services. Their experienced team of orthopedic surgeons, physical therapists, occupational therapists, general practitioners, and pain management specialists collaborate to deliver tailored treatment plans, combining advanced medical techniques with a compassionate approach. Whether you're seeking relief from acute pain, rehabilitation after an injury, or proactive management of chronic conditions, Premier Bone & Joint Centers is committed to improving your mobility and quality of life.

Description: Pain Care Centers is operated by a group of professionals committed to diagnosing and treating chronic pain and opioid dependency conditions. Chronic pain is any pain longer than 12 weeks and includes Back Pain, Diabetic Neuropathy, Arthritis, Foot, Leg & Knee Pain, Cancer Pain, Hand, Arm and Shoulder Pain, Headaches, etc. We offer the full spectrum of options to manage and control your condition, such as pain medication management including non-opioid medications and proper management of opioid-based medications. We also will educate & provide you on interventional therapy options such as Spinal Injections, Nerve Blocks, Stem Cell Therapy, Rhizotomy and Spinal Cord Stimulators. We help opioid dependent patients with Suboxone program.

Description:
At Cheyenne Regional, we believe the responsibility for health is bigger than one person.

When you trust our family to care for your family, our passionate physicians, nurses and staff will be here to encourage you throughout the healing process--with confidence, compassion and a personal touch.

We know our region better than any other healthcare system, and we're committed to providing you with the exceptional care you seek and deserve.

Our comprehensive line of healthcare services includes Cardiovascular, Cancer, Orthopedics, Neurosciences, Women and Children's Services, Trauma, Wound Management & Hyperbaric Medicine, Rehabilitation, Home Care, Hospice, Behavioral Health, Medical Imaging and Lab Services.

Description:
Dr. Trevor Gessel is a fellowship-trained sports medicine physiatrist at Casper Orthopedics. He specializes in providing nonoperative and minimally invasive orthopedic sports medicine care for a variety of musculoskeletal and peripheral neurological disorders.

Dr. Gessel has undergone additional training in interventional procedures of the lumbar spine and in using EMG and ultrasound to diagnose disorders. He is an expert in concussion management and in performing radiofrequency ablations, blocks, extracorporeal shockwave therapy, and a variety of injections, including peripheral joint steroid injections.

Dr. Gessel is available to see patients with a variety of musculoskeletal and peripheral neurological disorders at our Casper office.

Description: HealthSource Chiropractic offers natural pain relief solutions for patients in Riverton,WY, and the surrounding areas. We understand that every patient is unique and requires personalized care. That's why we take the time to assess your individual needs and develop a treatment plan that works for you. Our goal is to help you achieve optimal health and wellness through chiropractic care. Whether you're suffering from chronic pain, back pain, headaches, sciatica, or joint problems, we're here to help. With years of experience and a commitment to patient-centered care, you can trust us to provide effective, safe, and natural solutions to your health concerns. Don't let pain control your life. Contact us today to schedule!

Description:
At Cheyenne Regional, we believe the responsibility for health is bigger than one person.

When you trust our family to care for your family, our passionate physicians, nurses and staff will be here to encourage you throughout the healing process--with confidence, compassion and a personal touch.

We know our region better than any other healthcare system, and we're committed to providing you with the exceptional care you seek and deserve.

Our comprehensive line of healthcare services includes Cardiovascular, Cancer, Orthopedics, Neurosciences, Women and Children's Services, Trauma, Wound Management & Hyperbaric Medicine, Rehabilitation, Home Care, Hospice, Behavioral Health, Medical Imaging and Lab Services.

Description:
At Cheyenne Regional, we believe the responsibility for health is bigger than one person.

When you trust our family to care for your family, our passionate physicians, nurses and staff will be here to encourage you throughout the healing process--with confidence, compassion and a personal touch.

We know our region better than any other healthcare system, and we're committed to providing you with the exceptional care you seek and deserve.

Our comprehensive line of healthcare services includes Cardiovascular, Cancer, Orthopedics, Neurosciences, Women and Children's Services, Trauma, Wound Management & Hyperbaric Medicine, Rehabilitation, Home Care, Hospice, Behavioral Health, Medical Imaging and Lab Services.

Description: HealthFirst is a medical practice that blends the best of traditional and alternative medicine with compassion and genuine concern at their offices in the Greater Denver Area and Cheyenne, Wyoming. Led by holistic medicine physician, Jonathan W. Singer, DO, the team takes care to give each patient his personal attention and dedicates the time needed to get to the cause of complex issues. Dr. Singer received his bachelor's and master's degrees in food chemistry from the University of Wisconsin-Madison in Madison, Wisconsin. During that time, he invented an alternative to the food colorant Yellow No. 5, creating a natural option that's now standard in the food industry.

Description: HealthSource Chiropractic offers natural pain relief solutions for patients in Casper, WY, and the surrounding areas. We understand that every patient is unique and requires personalized care. That's why we take the time to assess your individual needs and develop a treatment plan that works for you. Our goal is to help you achieve optimal health and wellness through chiropractic care. Whether you're suffering from chronic pain, back pain, headaches, sciatica, or joint problems, we're here to help. With years of experience and a commitment to patient-centered care, you can trust us to provide effective, safe, and natural solutions to your health concerns. Don't let pain control your life. Contact us today to schedule!

Description:
Our Mission
At Symbii Home Health and Hospice, we strive to provide excellent care for individuals of all ages and in all stages of life. Our goal is to help you maintain the highest quality of life in the comfort of your own home. We understand the importance of family and we do our best to treat your family like our own. We are here to support, listen, and respond to your care with compassion and understanding

Symbii
